room_title: Escape room "POD" by A Narrow Escape in Hot Springs
room_address: 801 Central Ave Suite 35, Hot Springs, AR 71901
room_description: You and up to four friends find yourselves aboard an alien ship with no idea as to why you have been captured. Using the items around you, you must attempt to access and pilot the alien escape pod back to Earth. But hurry! You only have one hour before the escape pod becomes inactive. Will you make a narrow escape?
